  {
    "user": "UJBAJNFLK",
    "type": "message",
    "ts": "1755967109.853759",
    "client_msg_id": "2154e9ae-efa4-4e6c-bc54-90087c307fce",
    "text": "&gt; I haven’t personally seen a lot of languages being “pushed” onto “unsuspecting newbies”.\nLook at the Web site of just about every programming language that has one. They all advertise their great features, say nothing about limitations, and more importantly, mostly don't mention the type of software for which they were designed, leaving the usually false impression of \"general purpose\".",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1755690734.548889",
    "parent_user_id": "UMQ6LR9NZ",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "Ly7q3",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_quote",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I haven’t personally seen a lot of languages being “pushed” onto “unsuspecting newbies”."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Look at the Web site of just about every programming language that has one. They all advertise their great features, say nothing about limitations, and more importantly, mostly don't mention the type of software for which they were designed, leaving the usually false impression of \"general purpose\"."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "channel_name": "linking-together",
    "channel_id": "C5U3SEW6A"
  },
  {
    "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "type": "message",
    "ts": "1755974287.356829",
    "edited": {
      "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
      "ts": "1755974571.000000"
    },
    "client_msg_id": "f1ac2074-9ad5-4935-bece-b161237bcd5d",
    "text": "I'm with Josh here. Random languages are not getting distribution to newbies. Facebook and Google and whatnot have the newbies sewed up tight. And even the people who see the website run into limitations quickly enough. Most visitors to languages bounce, unconvinced.\n\nThere are plenty of problems in the world. It's not clear that more languages increases or decreases them.",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1755690734.548889",
    "parent_user_id": "UMQ6LR9NZ",
    "blocks": [
      {
